Flame Dragon II The Mystery of Golden City

Flame dragon is a classic strategy game developed in 1997 in Taiwan. This is a clone
on iOS, implemented based on Cocos-2d framework.
All of the resources, e.g. images, animations, musics, are borrowed from the origin
game.
Thanks for the support from:

Tieba: http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%D1%D7%C1%FA%C6%EF%CA%BF%CD%C5&fr=ala0&pstbala=1
FD Family: http://www.pcgamelab.net/fdfamily


目前第二关的开发工作已经进入测试阶段，我已经把源代码上传到github
https://github.com/Toneyisnow/FlameDragon

有需要的同学可以自行下载并编译运行。同时使用github也便于大家查看开发进度，跟踪相关改动。

